        <item>
            <title>中国技师手工研磨达 5 纳米精度，网民：离徙手造晶片不远了</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/12/5nm/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=5nm</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/12/5nm/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 10:00:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1235184</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>根据中国中央电视台报道，最近中国航天科工二院一名特级技师，成功以手工方式将超薄材料研磨至 5 纳米的精度。央视报导后引起网民广泛讨论，认为这意味著中国距离手工制造晶片不远。</p><p>根据中国央视报导，特级技师叶辉将超薄材料钽片研磨到 5 纳米级别，只有特殊仪器才能检测，被许多人赞誉为比机器还要厉害，成为「大国工匠」的代表。报导指他为了追求更高的精度，特别将自己的指纹磨平，以避免影响研磨的精细度。叶辉指高精度研磨需要的不仅是技术，更是一种对动作极致掌握的艺术，「一百下不如这一下，最后就是这一下推出来了」。这种匠心精神在当今机器大量代替人工的时代，显得尤为珍贵。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235187" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/001_001micronachieve-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/001_001micronachieve-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/001_001micronachieve-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>然而，报导也引来网民热话。有人认为，叶辉的技术意味著中国即将能够「手搓」出晶片。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1235185" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024051231310-694x370.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="370" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024051231310-694x370.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024051231310.jpg 1188w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>对此，央视在微博中特别澄清，叶辉达到的 5 纳米精度是指物件表面的粗糙度，而非晶片制造中的宽度。这种混淆可能来自于对半导体制造技术的误解，晶片的 5 纳米通常是指晶圆集成电路刻线的宽度，而非表面粗糙度。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_19870"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nopMi8NghfM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：YouTube</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/12/5nm/fun-tech/">中国技师手工研磨达 5 纳米精度，网民：离徙手造晶片不远了</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
